# Day 17/60 – AI Vehicle Cost & Fuel Analysis Dashboard

## Overview
Built an AI-powered Vehicle Cost & Fuel Analysis Dashboard that transforms vehicle data into meaningful insights through interactive visualizations and analytics.

## Features
- Cost per KM Analysis
- Fuel Cost Comparison
- Maintenance Cost Tracking
- CO₂ Emission Analysis
- Age-Based Vehicle Insights
- E85 Economics & Break-Even Analysis
- KPI Cards
- Responsive Dashboard Design

## Technologies Used
- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript
- SVG Charts
- Data Analytics

## Key Learnings
- Data visualization techniques
- KPI dashboard design
- Fuel efficiency analysis
- Cost optimization concepts
- Interactive dashboard development

## Project Outcome
Successfully created a dashboard capable of analyzing vehicle operating costs, fuel efficiency, maintenance expenses, and environmental impact metrics.

